I can't catch sight of his face
我看不见他的脸庞
Be perplexed on the bow of a tall back figure
高大的背影在船头迷茫
Where shall we go toward else?
我们会驶向何方？  
The heart，is on the sea like a rover
心，在大海中流浪

Bonnie wind，please get rid of the dark cloud
风儿啊，驱散那些乌黑的云
Let the starlight throw tender guide
让星光抛出温柔的牵引
And give correct directions in the wild
为我们指点迷津

Is the night thicker here?
在这里，夜会很深吗？
Is the sea colder here?
在这里，海会更冷吗？
Do you lose your dream after eyes closed?
闭上眼，你会失去梦想吗？
Or do you get the truth when eyes opened?
睁开眼，你会看到真实吗？

Bonnie wind，please raise my long hairs
风儿啊，卷起我的长发
All the answers become stars over the sky
所有的答案，化作漫天的星星
And slide slowly in your eyes
在你的注目礼下，冉冉滑行

But，but——
可是可是——
Would the heaven grant your holding of extraordinary brave
既然上天赐予我非凡的勇气
why it forced you to be distressed in love
为何要用爱苦苦相逼
Or there is allowed we stay together from being parted
如果上天让我们形影不离
why it drove us to a hopeless field
又为何将两人陷于绝境

Bonnie wind，please raise my skirt
风儿啊，扬起我的裙
I know the sun must rise
我知道太阳终将升起
Light
光明——
And shadow
倩影——
that wave in the burning wind
在燃烧的风中飘忽不定

When the dream that unable to catch  has flown over the sky
当天空放飞了捉不住的梦
When the miserable shadow has been buried on the sea
当大海殡葬了痛苦的影
When our heart has reached the echo of truth
当我们的心，去叩击真理的回音

Bonnie wind，please face round yourself
风儿啊，请侧转你的脸庞
I have seen your bright eyes
我看见你的明眸
in crazy wind
在不羁的风中
that flow the hopeful light
流转着希望之光——

Miracle of light
奇迹之光！


注：将之前写过的诗中译英，为无韵自由体。
